description: A library of icons (legacy 16x16, legacy 32x32 and SVG - vector for unified interface) that can be used for custom D365 CE entities. SVG Icons made by www.flaticon.com/authors/freepik from www.flaticon.com. The icons will be install to ZD365DT-Icons folder of the .NET Framework project when the NuGet is install. NOTE: NuGet content files copy is not supported on a .NET Core project.
title: ZD365.DeploymentTool.Icons
